memberdef.name: USING_TYPETRAIT_V
memberdef.initializer: template<class T> static constexpr bool trait##_v = trait<T>::value;

memberdef.name: USING_TYPETRAIT_T
memberdef.initializer: template<class T> using trait##_t = typename trait<T>::type;

memberdef.name: USING_STD_TYPETRAIT_BINARY
memberdef.initializer: template<class A, class B> using trait = std::trait<A, B>; \ template<class A, class B> static constexpr bool trait##_v = trait<A, B>::value;
